      <title>Modelo Bayesiano do Zero</title>
      <link>https://gomesfellipe.github.io/post/2018-07-28-modelo-bayesiano-do-zero/modelo-bayesiano-do-zero/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Jul 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
